)F FUNCTION -
  THE ASK COMMAND IS USED IN A CLIST TO DISPLAY A QUESTION AND REQUEST
  A YES OR NO REPLY.  A RETURN CODE OF 0 IS SET FOR YES AND 4 FOR NO.
    USE THIS COMMAND WITH SYSRC TO PROVIDE CLIST BRANCHING CAPABILITY.
)X SYNTAX -
         ASK 'TEXT'
  REQUIRED - 'TEXT'
  DEFAULTS - NONE
)O OPERANDS -
  'TEXT' - TEXT TO BE SENT TO THE TERMINAL
           IF THE QUESTION CONTAINS A QUOTATION MARK, TWO QUOTATION
           MARKS MUST BE ENTERED.
